(no particular order)

- Syslog
- Handle stdin, stdout, stderr, and all other file descriptors
- Command domain socket
  - Load/unload a process definition.
  - Temporarily suspend a process (stop for a while, then restart)
  - Ask for status on running processes.
- A proper shutdown sequence
- setsid
- Cleanup after a process dies (child processes by group)
- YAML properties (and appropriate functionality)
  - Location of PID file
  - Start dir
  - chroot
  - group id
  - rlimits
  - niceness
  - name
  - active flag
  - provides
  - requires
  - environment
  - umask
  - throttle interval
